<item>
 <title>Espaços de inovação na América Latina</title>
 <link>http://redelabs.org/blog/espa%C3%A7os-de-inova%C3%A7%C3%A3o-na-am%C3%A9rica-latina</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;A &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.asme.org/&quot;&gt;American Society of Mechanical Engineers&lt;/a&gt; desenvolveu uma &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1tB539S7lH8lWxV0UtGOTOsEqJetopnxdN-qv6W6SZxw/edit#gid=376384670&quot;&gt;lista pública de espaços de inovação na América Latina&lt;/a&gt;, em colaboração com a consultora &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.anansegroup.com/&quot;&gt;Ananse Group&lt;/a&gt;. A lista é aberta e podem ser adicionadas novas iniciativas. Os projetos são inseridos posteriormente no &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.anansegroup.com/mapping.html&quot;&gt;mapa global de espaços de inovação&lt;/a&gt;, que inclui experiências no mundo inteiro.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-2 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Categoria:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wordpress-category/espacos&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;espaços&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2016 18:03:09 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>lulaflei</dc:creator>
